OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fcontinues to clear the southeast, with
OL,7,Fblustery showers elsewhere, especially
OL,8,Fin the northwest. Some of these will
OL,9,Fbe locally heavy and wintry across
OL,10,Fnorthern hills. Showers easing in the
OL,11,Fsouth by dawn, with clear spells
OL,12,Fdeveloping. Turning chilly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FScattered showers at first,
OL,15,Fthen cloud building with outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain spreading across the country,
OL,17,Fthough staying mostly dry in the far
OL,18,Fsoutheast. Breezy, especially along
OL,19,Fthe hills and coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
